SQL: SELECT "item"."i_color", COUNT(*) as agg_0, COUNT(*) as agg_1 FROM "promotion" LEFT OUTER JOIN "item" ON "promotion"."p_item_sk" = "item"."i_item_sk"  WHERE "promotion"."p_promo_name" IN ('ese', 'anti', 'bar', 'pri', 'eing', 'able') GROUP BY "item"."i_color" ORDER BY "item"."i_color";
SELECT "date_dim"."d_fy_year", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "date_dim"  WHERE "date_dim"."d_current_day" = 'N' GROUP BY "date_dim"."d_fy_year" ORDER BY "date_dim"."d_fy_year";

SELECT "store_sales"."ss_quantity", COUNT(*) as agg_0, COUNT(*) as agg_1 FROM "store_returns" LEFT OUTER JOIN "store_sales" ON "store_returns"."sr_ticket_number" = "store_sales"."ss_ticket_number" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer_demographics" ON "store_sales"."ss_cdemo_sk" = "customer_demographics"."cd_demo_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "time_dim" ON "store_returns"."sr_return_time_sk" = "time_dim"."t_time_sk"  WHERE CAST("store_sales"."ss_ext_discount_amt" AS varchar) LIKE '%0.0%' AND CAST("store_returns"."sr_return_quantity" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%1%.0%' AND CAST("customer_demographics"."cd_credit_rating" AS varchar) LIKE '%R%isk%' GROUP BY "store_sales"."ss_quantity" ORDER BY "store_sales"."ss_quantity";

SELECT "call_center"."cc_mkt_desc", "catalog_sales"."cs_ship_mode_sk", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "customer" LEFT OUTER JOIN "catalog_returns" ON "customer"."c_customer_sk" = "catalog_returns"."cr_returning_customer_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "household_demographics" ON "customer"."c_current_hdemo_sk" = "household_demographics"."hd_demo_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "catalog_sales" ON "customer"."c_customer_sk" = "catalog_sales"."cs_bill_customer_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "call_center" ON "catalog_returns"."cr_call_center_sk" = "call_center"."cc_call_center_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "store_returns" ON "household_demographics"."hd_demo_sk" = "store_returns"."sr_hdemo_sk"  WHERE "household_demographics"."hd_buy_potential" IN ('0-500', '501-1000', '5001-10000') AND (CAST("catalog_sales"."cs_ship_date_sk" AS varchar) LIKE '%2450883%.0%' OR "catalog_sales"."cs_call_center_sk" IS NOT NULL OR CAST("catalog_sales"."cs_ship_date_sk" AS varchar) LIKE '%245088%5.0%') GROUP BY "call_center"."cc_mkt_desc", "catalog_sales"."cs_ship_mode_sk" ORDER BY "call_center"."cc_mkt_desc", "catalog_sales"."cs_ship_mode_sk";

SELECT "catalog_returns"."cr_refunded_hdemo_sk", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "catalog_returns"  WHERE CAST("catalog_returns"."cr_reason_sk" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%23.0%' AND CAST("catalog_returns"."cr_refunded_cash" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%0.0%' AND CAST("catalog_returns"."cr_return_quantity" AS varchar) LIKE '%15.%0%' AND CAST("catalog_returns"."cr_call_center_sk" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%7%.0%' AND "catalog_returns"."cr_reason_sk" = 20 GROUP BY "catalog_returns"."cr_refunded_hdemo_sk" ORDER BY "catalog_returns"."cr_refunded_hdemo_sk";

SELECT "store_sales"."ss_sold_date_sk", "store"."s_store_id", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "store_returns" LEFT OUTER JOIN "store" ON "store_returns"."sr_store_sk" = "store"."s_store_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "store_sales" ON "store_returns"."sr_item_sk" = "store_sales"."ss_item_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer_demographics" ON "store_sales"."ss_cdemo_sk" = "customer_demographics"."cd_demo_sk"  WHERE CAST("store_sales"."ss_store_sk" AS varchar) LIKE '%26.0%' AND CAST("customer_demographics"."cd_credit_rating" AS varchar) LIKE '%Ris%k%' GROUP BY "store_sales"."ss_sold_date_sk", "store"."s_store_id" ORDER BY "store_sales"."ss_sold_date_sk", "store"."s_store_id";

SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0, COUNT(*) as agg_1 FROM "income_band" LEFT OUTER JOIN "household_demographics" ON "income_band"."ib_income_band_sk" = "household_demographics"."hd_income_band_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "catalog_returns" ON "household_demographics"."hd_demo_sk" = "catalog_returns"."cr_refunded_hdemo_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "reason" ON "catalog_returns"."cr_reason_sk" = "reason"."r_reason_sk"  WHERE "catalog_returns"."cr_call_center_sk" IN (3, 5, 8, 4, 2, 6) AND "income_band"."ib_upper_bound" IN (200000, 150000, 100000, 140000, 10000, 130000, 50000, 170000, 30000, 80000, 40000, 60000) AND CAST("reason"."r_reason_desc" AS varchar) LIKE '%t%he%';

SELECT "date_dim"."d_current_week", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "web_page" LEFT OUTER JOIN "date_dim" ON "web_page"."wp_access_date_sk" = "date_dim"."d_date_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "catalog_sales" ON "date_dim"."d_date_sk" = "catalog_sales"."cs_ship_date_sk"  WHERE "date_dim"."d_current_year" != 'N' AND ("date_dim"."d_week_seq" IN (2136, 3210, 1572, 1436, 829, 2069, 2294, 3959, 675) OR "date_dim"."d_week_seq" != 2136) AND "catalog_sales"."cs_quantity" IN (79) AND "catalog_sales"."cs_sold_date_sk" IN (2451491, 2452236, 2452640, 2452611, 2452639, 2451161, 2452270, 2452610, 2451130, 2451543) GROUP BY "date_dim"."d_current_week" ORDER BY "date_dim"."d_current_week";

SELECT "item"."i_manufact", "store_sales"."ss_promo_sk", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "store_sales" LEFT OUTER JOIN "time_dim" ON "store_sales"."ss_sold_time_sk" = "time_dim"."t_time_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "item" ON "store_sales"."ss_item_sk" = "item"."i_item_sk"  WHERE CAST("time_dim"."t_meal_time" AS varchar) LIKE '%b%reakfast%' AND "item"."i_brand_id" != 5004001 AND "store_sales"."ss_quantity" IN (17, 61, 39, 31, 30, 76, 49) AND "item"."i_manufact_id" IN (18, 87, 71, 295, 193, 116) AND "time_dim"."t_minute" = 28 GROUP BY "item"."i_manufact", "store_sales"."ss_promo_sk" ORDER BY "item"."i_manufact", "store_sales"."ss_promo_sk";

SELECT "ship_mode"."sm_ship_mode_id", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "catalog_returns" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer_address" ON "catalog_returns"."cr_refunded_addr_sk" = "customer_address"."ca_address_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "ship_mode" ON "catalog_returns"."cr_ship_mode_sk" = "ship_mode"."sm_ship_mode_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "catalog_sales" ON "catalog_returns"."cr_order_number" = "catalog_sales"."cs_order_number" LEFT OUTER JOIN "warehouse" ON "catalog_sales"."cs_warehouse_sk" = "warehouse"."w_warehouse_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "date_dim" ON "catalog_sales"."cs_ship_date_sk" = "date_dim"."d_date_sk"  WHERE "customer_address"."ca_county" != 'Clark County' GROUP BY "ship_mode"."sm_ship_mode_id" ORDER BY "ship_mode"."sm_ship_mode_id";

SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0, COUNT(*) as agg_1 FROM "call_center" LEFT OUTER JOIN "date_dim" ON "call_center"."cc_closed_date_sk" = "date_dim"."d_date_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "catalog_returns" ON "call_center"."cc_call_center_sk" = "catalog_returns"."cr_call_center_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "item" ON "catalog_returns"."cr_item_sk" = "item"."i_item_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "catalog_page" ON "catalog_returns"."cr_catalog_page_sk" = "catalog_page"."cp_catalog_page_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "inventory" ON "date_dim"."d_date_sk" = "inventory"."inv_date_sk"  WHERE "date_dim"."d_month_seq" IN (132, 926, 940, 124, 155, 422, 462, 54, 383, 282, 451, 234, 700, 870, 232, 448, 635) AND "catalog_page"."cp_end_date_sk" IN (2451999, 2451329, 2452638, 2451543, 2450934, 2451479, 2451784, 2452365, 2451178, 2452273, 2451754, 2451726, 2451908, 2452821, 2451724, 2452091, 2452456, 2451361, 2450996) AND CAST("catalog_page"."cp_department" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%D%EPARTMENT%' AND "catalog_page"."cp_type" != 'monthly' AND CAST("catalog_returns"."cr_call_center_sk" AS varchar) LIKE '%1.0%';

SELECT "web_sales"."ws_promo_sk", "catalog_returns"."cr_warehouse_sk", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "time_dim" LEFT OUTER JOIN "catalog_returns" ON "time_dim"."t_time_sk" = "catalog_returns"."cr_returned_time_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_sales" ON "time_dim"."t_time_sk" = "web_sales"."ws_sold_time_sk"  WHERE "catalog_returns"."cr_returning_hdemo_sk" != 6809 AND "web_sales"."ws_ship_date_sk" IN (2452643, 2451911, 2451547) AND (CAST("time_dim"."t_minute" AS varchar) LIKE '%15%' OR CAST("time_dim"."t_sub_shift" AS varchar) LIKE '%afternoon%') GROUP BY "web_sales"."ws_promo_sk", "catalog_returns"."cr_warehouse_sk" ORDER BY "web_sales"."ws_promo_sk", "catalog_returns"."cr_warehouse_sk";

SELECT "store_returns"."sr_reason_sk", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "item" LEFT OUTER JOIN "store_returns" ON "item"."i_item_sk" = "store_returns"."sr_item_sk"  WHERE "item"."i_current_price" = 4.59 AND CAST("item"."i_class" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%pants%' AND CAST("store_returns"."sr_return_amt_inc_tax" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%0%.0%' AND CAST("item"."i_brand_id" AS varchar) LIKE '%100%4001.0%' AND CAST("item"."i_rec_end_date" AS varchar) LIKE '%1999-10%-27%' GROUP BY "store_returns"."sr_reason_sk" ORDER BY "store_returns"."sr_reason_sk";

SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "promotion" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_sales" ON "promotion"."p_promo_sk" = "web_sales"."ws_promo_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_returns" ON "web_sales"."ws_order_number" = "web_returns"."wr_order_number" LEFT OUTER JOIN "household_demographics" ON "web_sales"."ws_bill_hdemo_sk" = "household_demographics"."hd_demo_sk"  WHERE ("web_returns"."wr_web_page_sk" IN (109, 121, 43, 7, 67, 175) OR ("web_returns"."wr_web_page_sk" IN (121, 55, 139, 85, 223, 157, 169, 217, 67, 109, 43, 25, 37, 79, 151, 175) AND "web_returns"."wr_web_page_sk" IN (151, 169, 55, 121, 223, 7, 217, 139, 91, 157, 175, 37))) AND "promotion"."p_channel_dmail" = 'Y' AND "web_returns"."wr_returning_hdemo_sk" = 6170;

SELECT "customer_address"."ca_country", "catalog_sales"."cs_catalog_page_sk", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "customer_address" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_sales" ON "customer_address"."ca_address_sk" = "web_sales"."ws_bill_addr_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "catalog_sales" ON "customer_address"."ca_address_sk" = "catalog_sales"."cs_bill_addr_sk"  WHERE "web_sales"."ws_ship_date_sk" IN (2451182) AND CAST("customer_address"."ca_state" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%S%C%' AND CAST("catalog_sales"."cs_call_center_sk" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%4.%0%' GROUP BY "customer_address"."ca_country", "catalog_sales"."cs_catalog_page_sk" ORDER BY "customer_address"."ca_country", "catalog_sales"."cs_catalog_page_sk";

SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "income_band" LEFT OUTER JOIN "household_demographics" ON "income_band"."ib_income_band_sk" = "household_demographics"."hd_income_band_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_returns" ON "household_demographics"."hd_demo_sk" = "web_returns"."wr_returning_hdemo_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer_address" ON "web_returns"."wr_refunded_addr_sk" = "customer_address"."ca_address_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_sales" ON "web_returns"."wr_order_number" = "web_sales"."ws_order_number"  WHERE CAST("household_demographics"."hd_buy_potential" AS varchar) LIKE '%0-500%' AND CAST("customer_address"."ca_location_type" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%cond%o%' AND "income_band"."ib_upper_bound" != 110000 AND CAST("household_demographics"."hd_income_band_sk" AS varchar) LIKE '%14%' AND ("web_sales"."ws_ship_hdemo_sk" = 2477 OR "web_sales"."ws_ship_hdemo_sk" IN (5721, 5711, 1651, 4639, 2954, 4481, 2477, 6191, 3375, 2994, 2167, 4115, 5397, 6120, 3086, 658));

SELECT "household_demographics"."hd_income_band_sk", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "web_returns" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer_demographics" ON "web_returns"."wr_returning_cdemo_sk" = "customer_demographics"."cd_demo_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "household_demographics" ON "web_returns"."wr_refunded_hdemo_sk" = "household_demographics"."hd_demo_sk"  WHERE "web_returns"."wr_reason_sk" IN (5, 3, 16, 15, 1, 6, 12, 20, 26, 18, 33, 9, 34) AND "web_returns"."wr_return_quantity" != 4 GROUP BY "household_demographics"."hd_income_band_sk" ORDER BY "household_demographics"."hd_income_band_sk";

SELECT "date_dim"."d_current_year", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "web_page" LEFT OUTER JOIN "date_dim" ON "web_page"."wp_creation_date_sk" = "date_dim"."d_date_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "call_center" ON "date_dim"."d_date_sk" = "call_center"."cc_open_date_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "promotion" ON "date_dim"."d_date_sk" = "promotion"."p_start_date_sk"  GROUP BY "date_dim"."d_current_year" ORDER BY "date_dim"."d_current_year";

SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "household_demographics" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_sales" ON "household_demographics"."hd_demo_sk" = "web_sales"."ws_ship_hdemo_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_returns" ON "household_demographics"."hd_demo_sk" = "web_returns"."wr_refunded_hdemo_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "item" ON "web_sales"."ws_item_sk" = "item"."i_item_sk"  WHERE ("item"."i_class" != 'school-uniforms' OR "item"."i_container" = 'Unknown' OR "item"."i_class" = 'toddlers') AND "household_demographics"."hd_demo_sk" IN (829, 1572, 3414, 2162);

SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "web_site" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_sales" ON "web_site"."web_site_sk" = "web_sales"."ws_web_site_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "household_demographics" ON "web_sales"."ws_ship_hdemo_sk" = "household_demographics"."hd_demo_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_returns" ON "web_sales"."ws_order_number" = "web_returns"."wr_order_number"  WHERE CAST("web_sales"."ws_sales_price" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%0%.0%' AND CAST("web_site"."web_name" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%site_4%' AND CAST("web_site"."web_country" AS varchar) LIKE '%Unite%d%' AND "web_sales"."ws_promo_sk" IS NOT NULL;

SELECT "warehouse"."w_zip", COUNT(*) as agg_0, COUNT(*) as agg_1 FROM "inventory" LEFT OUTER JOIN "warehouse" ON "inventory"."inv_warehouse_sk" = "warehouse"."w_warehouse_sk"  WHERE "inventory"."inv_date_sk" IN (2450864, 2450836, 2450927, 2450892, 2450843, 2450913, 2450962, 2450885, 2450871, 2450906, 2450934) AND CAST("warehouse"."w_street_type" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%Dr.%' AND "warehouse"."w_gmt_offset" = -5.00 AND "warehouse"."w_warehouse_id" != 'AAAAAAAABAAAAAAA' GROUP BY "warehouse"."w_zip" ORDER BY "warehouse"."w_zip";

SELECT "date_dim"."d_month_seq", "call_center"."cc_company_name", COUNT(*) as agg_0, COUNT(*) as agg_1 FROM "call_center" LEFT OUTER JOIN "date_dim" ON "call_center"."cc_closed_date_sk" = "date_dim"."d_date_sk"  WHERE "date_dim"."d_moy" != 3 GROUP BY "date_dim"."d_month_seq", "call_center"."cc_company_name" ORDER BY "date_dim"."d_month_seq", "call_center"."cc_company_name";

SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "call_center" LEFT OUTER JOIN "date_dim" ON "call_center"."cc_closed_date_sk" = "date_dim"."d_date_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "store" ON "date_dim"."d_date_sk" = "store"."s_closed_date_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "promotion" ON "date_dim"."d_date_sk" = "promotion"."p_end_date_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "store_sales" ON "store"."s_store_sk" = "store_sales"."ss_store_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_site" ON "date_dim"."d_date_sk" = "web_site"."web_open_date_sk";

SELECT "warehouse"."w_warehouse_id", "customer"."c_birth_year", COUNT(*) as agg_0, COUNT(*) as agg_1 FROM "catalog_sales" LEFT OUTER JOIN "warehouse" ON "catalog_sales"."cs_warehouse_sk" = "warehouse"."w_warehouse_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "time_dim" ON "catalog_sales"."cs_sold_time_sk" = "time_dim"."t_time_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer_address" ON "catalog_sales"."cs_ship_addr_sk" = "customer_address"."ca_address_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "store_sales" ON "time_dim"."t_time_sk" = "store_sales"."ss_sold_time_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer" ON "customer_address"."ca_address_sk" = "customer"."c_current_addr_sk"  WHERE CAST("warehouse"."w_country" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%United%' AND CAST("catalog_sales"."cs_ship_date_sk" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%24508%91.0%' AND ("time_dim"."t_second" IN (28) OR "time_dim"."t_second" IN (47, 54) OR CAST("time_dim"."t_second" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%1%6%') AND ("time_dim"."t_minute" IN (0, 16, 28, 35, 43, 22, 15, 54) OR "time_dim"."t_minute" = 59) AND CAST("warehouse"."w_country" AS varchar) LIKE '%States%' GROUP BY "warehouse"."w_warehouse_id", "customer"."c_birth_year" ORDER BY "warehouse"."w_warehouse_id", "customer"."c_birth_year";

SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "store" LEFT OUTER JOIN "store_sales" ON "store"."s_store_sk" = "store_sales"."ss_store_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer_demographics" ON "store_sales"."ss_cdemo_sk" = "customer_demographics"."cd_demo_sk";

SELECT "reason"."r_reason_desc", "reason"."r_reason_sk", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "reason"  WHERE "reason"."r_reason_desc" = 'reason 24' AND "reason"."r_reason_id" IN ('AAAAAAAAJAAAAAAA', 'AAAAAAAADBAAAAAA', 'AAAAAAAAMAAAAAAA', 'AAAAAAAAIBAAAAAA', 'AAAAAAAALBAAAAAA', 'AAAAAAAAMBAAAAAA', 'AAAAAAAAKBAAAAAA', 'AAAAAAAAOBAAAAAA', 'AAAAAAAANBAAAAAA', 'AAAAAAAAOAAAAAAA', 'AAAAAAAAFAAAAAAA', 'AAAAAAAALAAAAAAA', 'AAAAAAAADCAAAAAA', 'AAAAAAAAIAAAAAAA', 'AAAAAAAABCAAAAAA', 'AAAAAAAAPAAAAAAA', 'AAAAAAAACCAAAAAA') AND CAST("reason"."r_reason_desc" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%N%ot%' AND "reason"."r_reason_sk" IN (28, 15, 7, 3, 30, 6, 35) GROUP BY "reason"."r_reason_desc", "reason"."r_reason_sk" ORDER BY "reason"."r_reason_desc", "reason"."r_reason_sk";

SELECT "date_dim"."d_current_year", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "call_center" LEFT OUTER JOIN "date_dim" ON "call_center"."cc_closed_date_sk" = "date_dim"."d_date_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "store_returns" ON "date_dim"."d_date_sk" = "store_returns"."sr_returned_date_sk"  WHERE ("date_dim"."d_current_year" != 'N' OR "date_dim"."d_quarter_name" IN ('1917Q3', '1960Q4', '1958Q3', '1936Q4', '1955Q3', '1908Q3', '1933Q3')) AND "store_returns"."sr_returned_date_sk" IS NOT NULL AND CAST("store_returns"."sr_return_quantity" AS varchar) LIKE '%20%.0%' GROUP BY "date_dim"."d_current_year" ORDER BY "date_dim"."d_current_year";

SELECT "customer_address"."ca_street_name", "web_returns"."wr_reason_sk", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "web_sales" LEFT OUTER JOIN "item" ON "web_sales"."ws_item_sk" = "item"."i_item_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_returns" ON "web_sales"."ws_order_number" = "web_returns"."wr_order_number" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer_address" ON "web_returns"."wr_refunded_addr_sk" = "customer_address"."ca_address_sk"  WHERE ("web_sales"."ws_warehouse_sk" IN (5) OR "web_sales"."ws_warehouse_sk" = 3) AND "item"."i_units" IN ('Oz', 'Case', 'Gross', 'Pound', 'Dram', 'Tsp', 'Tbl', 'Cup', 'Dozen', 'Ton', 'Box', 'Ounce', 'Pallet', 'Bundle', 'Carton', 'Each', 'N/A') GROUP BY "customer_address"."ca_street_name", "web_returns"."wr_reason_sk" ORDER BY "customer_address"."ca_street_name", "web_returns"."wr_reason_sk";

SELECT "reason"."r_reason_sk", "reason"."r_reason_desc", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "reason"  WHERE "reason"."r_reason_sk" = 16 AND "reason"."r_reason_desc" IN ('Did not get it on time', 'reason 29', 'reason 32', 'reason 37', 'duplicate purchase', 'No service location in my area', 'Found a better price in a store', 'reason 24', 'reason 31', 'reason 23') GROUP BY "reason"."r_reason_sk", "reason"."r_reason_desc" ORDER BY "reason"."r_reason_sk", "reason"."r_reason_desc";

SELECT "web_page"."wp_image_count", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "web_page"  WHERE "web_page"."wp_creation_date_sk" IS NOT NULL AND "web_page"."wp_type" = 'welcome' AND "web_page"."wp_web_page_id" != 'AAAAAAAAGNAAAAAA' GROUP BY "web_page"."wp_image_count" ORDER BY "web_page"."wp_image_count";

SELECT "web_page"."wp_customer_sk", "date_dim"."d_current_year", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "date_dim" LEFT OUTER JOIN "call_center" ON "date_dim"."d_date_sk" = "call_center"."cc_open_date_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "catalog_sales" ON "call_center"."cc_call_center_sk" = "catalog_sales"."cs_call_center_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_page" ON "date_dim"."d_date_sk" = "web_page"."wp_access_date_sk"  WHERE "call_center"."cc_open_date_sk" IN (2451063, 2450808, 2451024) AND "web_page"."wp_access_date_sk" IS NULL AND ("date_dim"."d_moy" = 3 OR "date_dim"."d_quarter_seq" IN (307)) AND "catalog_sales"."cs_quantity" != 93 GROUP BY "web_page"."wp_customer_sk", "date_dim"."d_current_year" ORDER BY "web_page"."wp_customer_sk", "date_dim"."d_current_year";

SELECT "time_dim"."t_hour", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "time_dim" LEFT OUTER JOIN "catalog_sales" ON "time_dim"."t_time_sk" = "catalog_sales"."cs_sold_time_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_returns" ON "time_dim"."t_time_sk" = "web_returns"."wr_returned_time_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "reason" ON "web_returns"."wr_reason_sk" = "reason"."r_reason_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer_address" ON "catalog_sales"."cs_bill_addr_sk" = "customer_address"."ca_address_sk"  WHERE "reason"."r_reason_id" != 'AAAAAAAABCAAAAAA' AND "reason"."r_reason_desc" IN ('Did not like the color', 'reason 27', 'reason 37', 'duplicate purchase', 'No service location in my area') AND CAST("web_returns"."wr_reason_sk" AS varchar) LIKE '%3%.0%' AND "catalog_sales"."cs_ship_mode_sk" IN (17, 13, 14, 20, 4, 6, 11, 2, 12, 9, 15, 8, 3, 10, 16, 19) AND CAST("customer_address"."ca_street_type" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%L%ane%' GROUP BY "time_dim"."t_hour" ORDER BY "time_dim"."t_hour";

SELECT "web_sales"."ws_warehouse_sk", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "web_returns" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_sales" ON "web_returns"."wr_order_number" = "web_sales"."ws_order_number"  WHERE "web_returns"."wr_returned_date_sk" = 2451285 AND "web_returns"."wr_web_page_sk" = 199 AND "web_sales"."ws_warehouse_sk" != 5 AND CAST("web_returns"."wr_reason_sk" AS varchar) LIKE '%2.%0%' GROUP BY "web_sales"."ws_warehouse_sk" ORDER BY "web_sales"."ws_warehouse_sk";

SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "reason" LEFT OUTER JOIN "catalog_returns" ON "reason"."r_reason_sk" = "catalog_returns"."cr_reason_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "item" ON "catalog_returns"."cr_item_sk" = "item"."i_item_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "catalog_sales" ON "item"."i_item_sk" = "catalog_sales"."cs_item_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer_address" ON "catalog_returns"."cr_refunded_addr_sk" = "customer_address"."ca_address_sk"  WHERE "catalog_sales"."cs_ship_hdemo_sk" = 3807 AND CAST("reason"."r_reason_desc" AS varchar) LIKE '%Fo%und%';
